title: [COMPLETE] OCE Platform Maintenance - 2016-11-2 @ 0600 AEDT
body:
Hi Folks

We'll be doing some planned maintenance on the OCE servers tomorrow morning (Wednesday 2nd November)

Ranked Queues will be disabled at 0430 am AEDT (Sydney Time)
The servers will be shut down at 0600 AEDT for a 3 hour maintenance window, opening back up at 0900 AEDT.
We'll post here if there are any updates to the plan.

Cheers!
Mindstar
